title: NFL ATL: Mock drafting with Bucky Brooks!
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Mock drafting with Bucky Brooks!
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal and Marc Sessler -- dives head first into 2014 NFL Draft coverage with the help of big board extraordinaire and host of "College Football 24/7" Bucky Brooks.  Elsewhere, the gang finishes up its "Roster Reset" series with the NFC North.
